name: Bag
description: Clogged Mind  added Bags to the most impossible to reach places unless you re move the shirt. To create aesthetic over function. More and more clothing lines add new tricks to make the clothing pieces handier to stash somewhere, pockets to keep you warm at winter and to be stylish in the summer. Clogged Mind also implemented oversized folded pants to make another useless piece of fashion as these pants will always drag across the floor.
